{
  "_comment": "Phase 8 §4.3/§4.4 — seccomp profile for controlplane (sentinelcore HTTP API). Default-deny with explicit allowlist of syscalls the Go runtime needs + network + file I/O. Derived from the Docker default profile minus syscalls our binary does not exercise (mount, unshare, ptrace, etc.). Tighten further after 2-week auditd observation in staging.",
